        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 20 at 4:32PM MDT until July 20 at 4:45PM MDT by NWS Glasgow MT</headline>
        <description>At 432 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 7 miles west of
Flowing Wells Rest Area, or 27 miles east of Jordan, moving east at
35 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Circle, Nelson Creek Rec Area, Brockway, Flowing Wells Rest Area, Van
Norman, and Watkins.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
